Within this example, we display a "Google Satellite" map centered on The Eiffel Tower, France (<span id="options">longitude</span>: 2.294460 and <span id="options">latitude</span>: 48.858589) with a hight <span id="options">zoom</span> level(17).<br><br>
var m = new <a href="<?php echo $documentation_path;?>/WIND.html" target="_blank">WIND</a>.<a href="<?php echo $documentation_path;?>/WIND.Map.html" target="_blank">Map</a>('<span id="param">map</span>',{'<span id="options">type</span>': 'Google Satellite','<span id="options">name</span>': "Carte", '<span id="options">longitude</span>': 2.294460, '<span id="options">latitude</span>': 48.858589, '<span id="options">zoom</span>': 17, '<span id="options">header</span>': true, '<span id="options">color</span>': '#AEEE00', '<span id="options">border</span>': '#01B0F0 10px inset','<span id="options">icon</span>':"styles/images/mvizicon.png",'<span id="options">top</span>':50});<br><br>
Here we specify the <span id="options">name</span> of the map ("Carte").<br>
'<span id="options">header</span>': true, '<span id="options">color</span>': '#AEEE00' : Here we want to add a header to the map with a green color.<br>
'<span id="options">border</span>': '#01B0F0 10px inset': Here we customize the border's properties ( the color, the width and the style ).<br>
And lastly we indicate the <span id="options">icon</span>'s URL and the position ('<span id="options">top</span>':50).